{"tid":1582990,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外交部：不斷升級貿易戰正使美國加速失去中国市場份額","createTime":"2019-09-20T11:02:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T02:24:42.000Z","uid":184679,"like":18,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"28f8c737ae13d0912fbdf7174c6e5df976d74ddb","tid":1582990,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T11:02:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1481658_1_20190920184949.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1481658_1_20190920184949.jpg&h=d72e8149&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人耿爽說，不斷升級的貿易戰正在使美國加速失去中國市場份額，可謂損人害已，得不償失。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽在外交部的例行記者會，回應有關美中貿易全國委員會發布《2019年度國會選區對華出口報告》的提問，他說，報告反映出一段時間以來，美國工商界和地方對中美貿易摩擦加劇的擔憂，以及對中美雙方通過談判妥善解決經貿摩擦的期待。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽又說，中方希望美方多傾聽美國國內的理性聲音，同中方一起，在相互尊重、平等互利基礎上，為談成一個互利雙贏的協議作出努力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1481658-20190920.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1481658-20190920.htm&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8tMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=a693929a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1481658-20190920.htm&h=26c68038\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1481658-20190920.htm</a>"},{"pid":"23d51428a5dbad2af47cac7b0bafff2b7bcc0b5b","tid":1582990,"uid":76776,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T11:03:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d3a757862f1c4370f4d812e425c984ff91787ed4","tid":1582990,"uid":82359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T11:04:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc781d13f5be22ea05a9a8b012707cc2a26eb840","tid":1582990,"uid":274149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T11:04:24.000Z","msg":"人地好恨你個市場咩？你不如行出北京睇再小陸其他地方的經濟。拍緊蚊"},{"pid":"69d817